These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, pear, cucumber, zucchini
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani, italian, indian
1. the pakistani is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is the indian##1
3. the italian is on the right of the indonesian##1
4. the person eating pear is on the left of the indian##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | zucchini | cucumber | pear | cauliflower   |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | indonesian     | italian   | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, rock-climbing, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, basketball, rowing, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | baking | puzzles | card-games    |
| Sport   | rowing    | basketball      | skateboarding | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, sudoku, woodworking, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, spy, sports
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | camping | hiking | woodworking   | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | spy | sports | documentary         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, romance, zombie, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, weightlifting, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | romance | superhero  | zombie      |
| Sport         | water-polo | snowboarding   | weightlifting | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, nectarine, plum, lemon
4 different pets are kept: snake, bird, frog, lizard
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | lemon | plum | nectarine | peach |
| Pet    | snake       | lizard | frog | bird     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, egyptian, thai
4 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, bird, cat
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the thai is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the egyptian##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | brazilian | canadian |
| Pet           | ferret      | bird | cat | dog    |

