.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, pop, funk, punk
4 different pets are kept: bird, turtle, cat, goat
1. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
2. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
3. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
5. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop | trance | punk  |
| Pet           | cat | bird | goat       | turtle |

