.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, software-developer, architect, paramedic
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, bike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the software-developer##1
2. the person driving the train is the paramedic##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the engineer##1
4. the architect is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | architect | engineer      | software-developer | paramedic |
| Transport   | helicopter          | taxi | bike     | train    |

