The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, train, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | romance       | western | time-travel   |
| Transport     | subway | train | scooter   | bike |

