.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, coffee, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, helicopter, quad-bike, subway
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | 7up | coffee  | water | almond-milk |
| Transport   | subway | quad-bike | helicopter          | roller    |

