.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, funk, techno, reggae
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking tea is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | tea  | juice | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | techno | reggae           | funk   |

