The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, fantasy, superhero, satire
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | writing | sudoku | singing | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | superhero    | crime      | fantasy   |

