.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, french, colombian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, van, skateboard, trike
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the french##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the polish##1
3. the indonesian is on the left of the colombian##1
4. the polish is the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | indonesian | colombian | french | polish   |
| Transport     | skateboard  | tram    | van       | trike |

 